description.full: This game was classified by the community with the following category scores - Violence=0/3, Sex=0/3, Mature Content=0/3. Think you’re awesome with a football? How will you fare compared to the best on the global score boards? Easy to learn, difficult to master keepy-uppy and freestyle football trials, let’s see if you’re as good as you think you are.
